text:
Looking at your medical screening application, I can see this is a comprehensive tool with various assessment modules. The codebase appears well-structured with Next.js 14 App Router, TypeScript, and a professional UI using shadcn/ui components.

I notice you have several key assessment tools:
- Quick Screen for initial evaluation
- Red Flag Checker for critical symptoms
- Stand Test for physical assessment
- PEM Quest for post-exertional malaise
- Criteria Engine for diagnostic criteria
- Subtype Advisor for treatment guidance

What would you like me to help you with today? I can assist with:
- Adding new features or assessment tools
- Improving existing functionality
- Bug fixes or performance optimization
- UI/UX enhancements
- Integration with external services

What specific area would you like to work on?
